<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>ðŸš¨ Critical Security Alert</title>
  <style>
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; }
    .header { background: #dc2626; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 20px; background: #fff; }
    .alert-box { background: #fef2f2; border-left: 4px solid #dc2626; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .details { background: #f9fafb; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 15px 0; }
    .footer { background: #f3f4f6; padding: 15px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background: #dc2626; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 10px 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>ðŸš¨ CRITICAL SECURITY ALERT</h1>
      <p>Immediate attention required</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>
      
      <div class="alert-box">
        <h3>Security Alert Details</h3>
        <p><strong>Alert Type:</strong> <%= @alert.alert_type.humanize %></p>
        <p><strong>Severity:</strong> <span style="color: #dc2626; font-weight: bold;"><%= @alert.severity.upcase %></span></p>
        <p><strong>Time:</strong> <%= @alert.triggered_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p %Z") %></p>
        <p><strong>Message:</strong> <%= @alert.message %></p>
      </div>
      
      <% if @alert_data.present? %>
      <div class="details">
        <h4>Technical Details</h4>
        <% @alert_data.each do |key, value| %>
          <p><strong><%= key.to_s.humanize %>:</strong> <%= value %></p>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <% end %>
      
      <p>This is a critical security alert that requires immediate attention. Please:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Review the alert details above</li>
        <li>Check your recent account activity</li>
        <li>Change your password if you suspect unauthorized access</li>
        <li>Contact your system administrator if you have any concerns</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>
        <a href="<%= security_dashboard_url %>" class="button">View Security Dashboard</a>
      </p>
      
      <p>If you believe this alert is legitimate but expected, you can safely ignore this message. However, if you suspect unauthorized activity, please take immediate action to secure your account.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated security notification from BrokerSync.</p>
      <p>For support, contact your system administrator.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>